casebody.data:
Helen Hay WHITNEY et al. v. Dolores W. MERVILLE. No. 7284. Circuit Court of Appeals, Sixth Circuit. Nov. 10, 1937. Bulkley, Hauxhurst, Inglis & Sharp, of Cleveland, Ohio, for appellants. Krueger, Gorman & Davis, of Cleveland, Ohio, for appellee.

Before MOORMAN, HICKS, and SI-MONS, Circuit Judges.

*1023PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel, it is ordered that the appeal herein be, and the same is, dismissed at the costs of appellants.
